{"type": "article", "id": 3713, "title": "Horizon 蓝牙闹钟", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-20T07:43:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233216GPDWYSabTMRBo5yL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t凛冬将至，你需要一款贴心的闹钟在清晨把你从睡梦中唤醒。美国知名耳机厂商 JBL 近日推出了一款名为「 Horizon」的蓝牙闹钟，或者你也可以将它看作是一款扬声器。Horizon 配备了两个立体声输出但愿，背部设计为 LED 的床头灯功能。用户可以预设自己喜欢的音乐或是 FM 调频，然后配合着渐变的灯光，在设定的时间将自己唤醒，轻柔且浪漫。提供黑白两色可选，定价 99.95 美元，<a href=\"http://www.jbl.com/estore/jbl/us/products/JBL-Horizon/JBL%20HORIZON_JBL_US?skuId=JBLHORIZONBLKAM_JBL_US&amp;searchMode=regularProductOnly&amp;sCatId=cat570038\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233213yBxdm30zRhkToOnE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233214B1RZ4M9vtgrPOoT8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233214FZIn30i5g9xcfAP4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233215evG7CpyOkDr8F2Wa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}